    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes sense. but the way it's written here, it says i have to indemnify them against any third-party claims, like if someone says i stole their design. does that mean i'm basically on the hook for all their legal costs if they get sued because of my work?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
